    notes and <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Spaced_repetition">
    spaced repetition</a>.
  </p>
  <p class="text-xl">
    <%= link_to "Get started", new_user_registration_path, :class => "text-green-900 bg-green-100 p-2 rounded-md" %>
